16:53.240 --> 16:56.160
 or we get hung up on the meaning of what exactly

16:56.160 --> 16:57.520
 do we mean by freedom?

16:57.520 --> 16:59.800
 And can you have, can you be,

16:59.800 --> 17:02.200
 do we mean compatibilist free will,

17:02.200 --> 17:05.360
 libertarian free will, what do these things mean?

