 So if you could philosophize a little bit

20:25.280 --> 20:27.360
 within this empirical question,

20:27.360 --> 20:31.440
 at where do you think would enter the,

20:31.440 --> 20:33.840
 by which mechanism would enter the possibility

20:33.840 --> 20:35.600
 that we can't predict the outcome?

