 Okay, so what does quantum mechanics say about the world?

30:15.680 --> 30:18.560
 You know, the physicists, I think over the generations,

30:18.560 --> 30:21.200
 you know, convinced people that that is an unbelievably

30:21.200 --> 30:23.920
 complicated question and, you know, just give up

